      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It's clean, runs like a dream, and is just waiting for someone new to take it on an adventure. If you're looking for a dependable ride that's been well-loved, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
