    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for purchase is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis has been vetted with documented rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system refresh and valve lash adjustment. The suspension retains its communicative feedback with refreshed bushings and a balanced MacPherson/multi-link setup, offering a pure, analog performance profile for the discerning driver.",
